{"tid":2004394,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共菊梓喬 為上位棄良知","createTime":"2020-05-06T12:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T14:10:03.000Z","uid":306528,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac31e08692f35e77cc485c11cd2a8b7e7a97719","tid":2004394,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"呢個仆街菊梓喬之前已經擦鞋擦到上老細心口，趁吳若希生仔就搶走人哋星夢一姐地位，又成日扮到楚楚可憐、暗中透過傳媒暗讚自己踩低吳若希。<br />\n<br />\n今次TVB歌手齊唱奶共，佢就第一個衝出去奶，務求繼續得到老闆歡心。相反同公司其他女歌手，吳若希、譚嘉儀、戴祖儀全部都冇佢博上位博到咁離譜。<br />\n<br />\n以前就靠觀眾緣去彌補自己唱得難聽生得肉酸，今次佢就證明比大家睇佢個人係幾咁投機主義，良心比狗食咗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等變歪星啦菊梓喬</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"161f6cbd5891f7eaf851ebb3af47736515190000","tid":2004394,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂 仲做tvb嘅都係食屎狗黎"},{"pid":"bc11eb55372e3e6685ae0904c2427540e3b647d1","tid":2004394,"uid":6361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"首首歌旋律都係差唔多 聽得多都覺煩"},{"pid":"b949ebe417f1e6f8e7db3404cf5a5692133cbc8c","tid":2004394,"uid":51041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"mk妹look陳曉怡正好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白滑腳又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d67a09de8a13394e0dd3b1f58a48c6b34d2329","tid":2004394,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147e687b5dfcadd6cfc99a39c3d5f5e0fc326012","tid":2004394,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161f6cbd5891f7eaf851ebb3af47736515190000","tid":200